// Schema-driven inbox item rendering.
//
// ItemSchema defines everything the UI needs to render and interact with an
// inbox item: read-only display fields, input form fields with validation,
// and available action buttons. Any module can create inbox items with a
// schema payload and the inbox UI renders them generically — no custom
// per-type renderers needed.
